claim.claim-text:
1. An electric device having at least one liquid crystal display panel, said liquid crystal display panel comprising:
an active matrix circuit over a first region of a substrate;
at least one thin film transistor formed in said active matrix circuit, said at least one thin film transistor comprising a semiconductor layer and a gate electrode with a gate insulating film interposed therebetween;
a source or drain electrode electrically connected to said semiconductor layer;
a protrusion formed over a second region of said substrate, said protrusion comprising a first layer comprising a same material as said gate electrode a second layer comprising a same material as said source or drain electrode, and a third layer comprising a same material as said semiconductor layer; and
a sealing member over said protrusion,
wherein said first layer and said second layer overlap with each other and are insulated from each other.
